it has arrived! For all those who wern't, well, its here anyways.

I have already listed all the improvements in my initial release
announcement a week or two ago, so without further adeu, you may go grab
the binaries.

Have fun. Be sure to read the INSTALL file before reporting that it
doesn't work.
